messages.messageBody:
Everyone-

Some reminders for those who are undecided on some conference offerings:


6 August Hotel Reservations with conference
rate, after that the rate goes up considerably. I can do nothing about
the
increase after this date! Please
book your room in time!


10 August Late Registration for the conference.
After Aug 10, you will pay the "At the Door" fee. No exceptions!


10 August T-Shirt Order deadline. I will be
ordering a very few extras, but don't count on it!



10 August Banquet Reservations. We'll need your
reservations and payment for the Banquet


Hope this helps with your planning!



~Kelly

Kelly Lovejoy
Conference Coordinator
Live and Learn Unschooling Conference
http://liveandlearnconference.org
